1 offi ce may be scheduled on the same dates as the filing period for
2 state or federal office to be filled at such election.
3 F. Any school district, technology center district,
4 municipality, including any municipality governed by charter, rural
5 fire protection district or any other entity seeking to hold a
6 special election for the purpose of filling a vacancy shall schedule
7 a candidate filing period of three (3) days to begin not more than
8 twenty (20) days following the date the resolution calling the
9 election is required to be filed with the secretary of the county
10 election board.
11 SECTION 2. This act shall become effective November 1, 2025.
